Join Node: Add Related Columns of Data to the Recipe

Use a Join Node in the Recipe Canvas

When working with CRM Analytics datasets and external objects, add a join node on the recipe canvas. When working with Salesforce objects, you can either create a join on the recipe canvas or join the data when you first create your dataset on the Add Input Data screen.

Use a Join Node on the Add Input Data Screen (Salesforce Objects Only)
